author: Daniel Greene
description:
The entire Greenbone Saga — Jade City, Jade War, Jade Legacy — explained in one massive whiteboard session.
We’ll cover every clan war, betrayal, and family drama that defines one of modern fantasy’s best trilogies.

This video walks through the complete Kaul family story, the rise and fall of No Peak, and the political and personal rivalries that shaped Fonda Lee’s Greenbone Saga.
